---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Testimonial from '../components/Testimonial.astro';
import headshot from '../assets/headshot.jpg';
---

<Layout title="Home">
  <div>
    <p class="leading-relaxed mb-2">
      I'm Vignesh Mohankumar, and Nila is my independent consulting practice. I partner with technical leaders to ship production AI systems.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2 class="font-bold text-lg mb-4">Testimonials</h2>
    <div class="space-y-8">
      <Testimonial 
        quote="Vignesh helped our staff engineers build a strong understanding of applied AI and showed them how to use AI tools to speed up development in meaningful ways. He played a key role in shaping our AI roadmap, helping the team get clear on both what to build and how to build it. He also designed the systems that let us run all our models on internal infrastructure, ensuring customer data stays private and secure. His guidance helped us move faster in the near term while laying the groundwork for long-term growth in our AI capabilities."
        author="Paul Klicnik"
        role="CTO"
        company="Relay"
        url="https://relayfi.com"
      />
      
      <Testimonial 
        quote="Vignesh helped us get our AI system to production within a month with an architecture designed to support future product goals we had in mind. He set us up to improve our systems over time by building an evaluation system and upleveling our team on best practices in applied AI engineering."
        author="Patrick Vatterott"
        role="CTO"
        company="Vitally"
        url="https://vitally.io"
      />

      <Testimonial 
        quote="Vignesh helped our team understand where best to leverage AI in our platform and how to go about building and evaluating solutions. His guidance helped us separate the noise online from practical skills that matter."
        author="Jim ONeill"
        role="CTO"
        company="FinQore"
        url="https://finqore.com"
      />
      
      <Testimonial 
        quote="Our onboarding flow needed to capture user preferences in a natural and effective way. Vignesh experimented with generative AI approaches and developed a system that turned chatbot conversations into structured insights. His work was essential to delivering the experience we envisioned."
        author="Charles DePue"
        role="CEO"
        company="Sitch"
        url="https://joinsitch.com"
      />
      
      <Testimonial 
        quote="Our team needed to build a frontend interface for a conversational AI application for a large prospective customer on a tight timeline. Vignesh stepped in and integrated our chat SDK and NLX platform into a solution that could easily be productized. The solution worked to specification and was a key part of how we showcased our capabilities to the client. His ability to deliver under pressure made all the difference."
        author="Andrei Papancea"
        role="CEO"
        company="NLX"
        url="https://nlx.ai"
      />
      
      <Testimonial 
        quote="Vignesh helped us architect multiple complex features, explaining how to set up AI systems that could be measured and improved over time. His ability to consider the full range of options helped us find the right solution for problems we had, including running local, open-source and multi-modal models as needed."
        author="Kiran Cherukuri"
        role="Founder"
        company="Perdiem"
        url="https://perdiem.xyz"
      />
    </div>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2 class="font-bold text-lg mb-3">Background</h2>
    <p class="leading-relaxed mb-2">
      I've partnered with companies in industries including enterprise SaaS,
      consumer social, healthcare, fintech, and crypto.
    </p>
    <p class="leading-relaxed mb-2">
      Prior to consulting, I was an early engineer at two AI-driven companies
      that were acquired:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <strong>Drift:</strong> Conversational AI for marketing and sales
        (acquired by Vista Equity Partners for $1.2B)
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Kensho:</strong> AI for financial services (acquired by S&P
        Global for $550M)
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2 class="font-bold text-lg mb-3">Recent Content</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <a href="https://medium.com/relay-financial/how-we-built-ai-powered-expense-categorization-with-rag-23a640fa3e78" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">How We Built AI-Powered Expense Categorization with RAG</a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="https://maven.com/p/bb1c7b/cursor-for-ai-engineers" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Cursor for Staff Engineers</a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="https://nila.is/blog/ai-eng-terms/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">AI Engineering Terms, Simplified</a>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2 class="font-bold text-lg mb-3">About</h2>
    <div class="flex flex-col">
      <img 
        src={headshot.src} 
        alt="Vignesh Mohankumar" 
        class="w-40 mb-4"
        loading="lazy"
      />
      <div>
        <p class="leading-relaxed mb-2">
          I'm based in New York, NY. I grew up in New England and was born near Chennai, India. Nila means moon in my native language Tamil (my sister suggested the name).
        </p>
        <p class="leading-relaxed">
          Find me on 
          <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/vigxyz" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn</a>,
          <a href="https://x.com/vig_xyz" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">X</a>
          and my <a href="https://vig.xyz" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">personal blog</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
